{"tid":281168,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"白旗旗主鄭松泰內部通訊(完整版)","createTime":"2017-06-12T13:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T14:04:49.000Z","uid":33890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"368a0fc362b59a3f56aa0b62f45cc5f1f9a17f7f","tid":281168,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/passiontimes/videos/1486877618042067/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpassiontimes%2Fvideos%2F1486877618042067%2F&d=oApwOix428vnKSn3%2BW8N71eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=21c9d8ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/passiontimes/videos/1486877618042067/</a><br />\n【熱血公民主席鄭松泰內部通訊流出(完整版)】<br />\n熱血公民主席鄭松泰於上周五（9/6），在熱血公民工作組內進行直播，交待熱血公民未來發展方向。另外，鄭松泰亦就最近發生的糾紛，表達個人看法。<br />\n然而，有熱血公民成員，錄製直播片段，並將之流出。更將鄭松泰的說法斷章取義，抽出當中的片言隻語作出攻擊。<br />\n本報收到熱血公民提供的完整片段，發現坊間所節錄的片段，並不能完整表達鄭松泰的意思，故現放出完整片段，讓公眾觀賞，內容略嫌冗長，敬請原諒。<br />\n本報收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係同一班人咩?咩叫斷章取義?知唔知咩叫節錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔想比View可以睇呢條<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B4Bf5z6cPslYbWg1WUFPSmJ0am8/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F0B4Bf5z6cPslYbWg1WUFPSmJ0am8%2Fview&d=oApwOix428vnKSn3%2BW8N71eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=b02bd54d\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B4Bf5z6cPslYbWg1WUFPSmJ0am8/view</a>"},{"pid":"d84e0b142271aaf32c1952a445c026ddd996c5dd","tid":281168,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:40:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://forum12.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6736852\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum12.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D6736852&d=oApwOix428vnKSn3%2BW8N71eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=63b26650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum12.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&a